<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer5520166554086139184">In these ten interwoven stories, <i> </i>two adolescent brothers face a world in which their father has suddenly died, a world dominated by their beautiful and complicated mother. Thirty years later, one of the brothers-the only remaining survivor of a family he seeks both to leave behind and to preserve in words forever-narrates these precise and heartbreaking tales. Suffused wi</span>
  <span id="freeText5520166554086139184" style="display:none">In these ten interwoven stories, <i> </i>two adolescent brothers face a world in which their father has suddenly died, a world dominated by their beautiful and complicated mother. Thirty years later, one of the brothers-the only remaining survivor of a family he seeks both to leave behind and to preserve in words forever-narrates these precise and heartbreaking tales. Suffused with the beauty of Richard McCann's extraordinary language, <i> Mother of Sorrows </i>introduces us to an elegant writer like no other in contemporary fiction.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5520166554086139184" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

